section.section:
On or before March 1 of each year, an annual report that meets the specifications of paragraph (2) of this subsection shall be submitted to the Commissioner by:
each authorized insurer that provides health insurance in the State;
each nonprofit health service plan that is authorized by the Commissioner to operate in the State;
each health maintenance organization that is authorized by the Commissioner to operate in the State; and
as applicable in accordance with regulations adopted by the Commissioner, each managed care organization that is authorized to receive Medicaid prepaid capitation payments under Title 15, Subtitle 1 of the Health - General Article.

The data required under paragraph (2) of this subsection shall be reported:
by product delivery system for health benefit plans that are issued under Subtitle 12 of this title;
in the aggregate for health benefit plans that are issued to individuals;
in the aggregate for a managed care organization that operates under Title 15, Subtitle 1 of the Health - General Article; and
in a manner determined by the Commissioner in accordance with this subsection for all other health benefit plans.
